# Project

Next.js **16** · React **19** · Sanity **v6** · Tailwind **v4** · RTL Urdu · https://darulquran.pk

```bash
npm run dev      # :3001, /studio
npm run build    # prebuild stubs polyfills
npm run lint && npm run check:urdu
```

Env (never commit): `NEXT_PUBLIC_SANITY_*`, `SANITY_API_TOKEN`, `EMAIL_*`, `NEXT_PUBLIC_SITE_URL`

## Layout

```
app/
  (site)/          # public routes (no URL segment)
  studio/          # Sanity CMS
  api/             # route handlers
  icon.svg         # favicon fallback
components/
  layout/ ui/ sections/ content/ seo/ studio/
lib/
  types/           # NavNode, schema DTOs (no UI imports)
  seo.ts paths.ts cmsPage.ts …
sanity/
  schemaTypes/ lib/   # queries.ts, fetchers.ts, client.ts
public/            # static fallbacks only
scripts/ deploy/
```

- Thin `page.tsx` — fetch + compose; route-private UI in `app/**/_components/`
- Types in `lib/types/`; data layer must not import from `components/`
- `safeFetch` → Sanity; `revalidate = 300` on CMS routes
- Brand: `dq-*`; font: `DeferredUrduFont`
